structure.unit: DIVISION OF INSURANCE AND INSURANCE GENERALLY (Superseded)

law.history: Repealed 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 21, sec. 2. -- Amended 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 173, sec. 1, effective June 17, 1948. -- Created 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 202, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Investment of funds of domestic insurance companies in loans to war veterans and in certain corporate securities.
